      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_4",
      "block_index": 4,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "character_list",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "邹母：老旦",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 5,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_5",
      "block_index": 5,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "plot_summary",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "情节",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 2,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_6",
      "block_index": 6,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "plot_summary",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "唐德宗时，卢杞为相，权倾朝野，惟以陷害忠良为事。时吐谷浑入寇，卢杞使陈杏元之父，拒之雁门关。因兵力单薄，大败。卢杞请唐德宗将其女杏元赐予番王求和，以赎丧师之罪。杏元已许字梅生，其父迫于君命，",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 95,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_7",
      "block_index": 7,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "plot_summary",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "不得已允之。杏元痛哭就道，至落雁坡，投澜图尽。有神人化作旋风，吹至河南节度使邹伯符家园。适邹女云英游园见之，细询来历，杏元恐泻露机关，复遭不测，遂改名汪月英。邹女怜其漂泊无依，请母收为义",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 93,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_8",
      "block_index": 8,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "plot_summary",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "女。邹母喜纳之。后卢杞事败，有名将浑瑊李晟等，大败吐谷浑，而杏元仍归梅生偕老焉。",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 40,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_9",
      "block_index": 9,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "plot_summary",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "根据《戏考》第二册整理",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 11,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_10",
      "block_index": 10,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（邹云英、丫鬟同上。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_11",
      "block_index": 11,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "风吹铃儿响，荷花开满塘。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 12,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "引子"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_12",
      "block_index": 12,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "闺阁幼女不知愁，二八衣装上翠楼。身在秀房学针黹，侍奉老母到白头。（邹云英坐下。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 40,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "念"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_13",
      "block_index": 13,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "奴家邹云英。爹爹邹伯符，现任河南八府巡按。母亲诰封夫人。是我未曾随父到任，在家闷闷不乐。丫鬟，带路花园。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 44,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_15",
      "block_index": 15,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_丫鬟",
      "text": "是。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 2,
      "speaker_name_raw": "丫鬟",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_16",
      "block_index": 16,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "老爹爹在朝中官居爵禄，我母亲受诰封在家享荣华。耳边厢又听得风声响落，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "西皮慢板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_19",
      "block_index": 19,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（陈杏元上，矮坐地下。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 12,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_20",
      "block_index": 20,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "叫丫鬟看分明细对我说。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "西皮慢板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_21",
      "block_index": 21,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_丫鬟",
      "text": "启禀小姐：花园中有了妖怪了。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 14,
      "speaker_name_raw": "丫鬟",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_22",
      "block_index": 22,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "有这等事？待我看来。哪里是妖怪，那旁边是一顽石，你我坐在一旁，听她讲些什么。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 10,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_24",
      "block_index": 24,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "苦吓！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 3,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_25",
      "block_index": 25,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "陈杏元身投在落雁坡下，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "反二黄慢板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_26",
      "block_index": 26,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "耳边厢又听得走石飞砂。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_27",
      "block_index": 27,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "猛然间睁开眼太湖石下，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_28",
      "block_index": 28,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "那一旁坐定了观音菩萨。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_29",
      "block_index": 29,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "适才间奴投澜一心无假，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_30",
      "block_index": 30,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "昏沉沉也不知落在谁家？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_31",
      "block_index": 31,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "你不是妖魔鬼怪？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 8,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_32",
      "block_index": 32,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "本非是妖魔怪休要惊怕，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "反二黄慢板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_33",
      "block_index": 33,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "你不是妖魔鬼怪，你是甚等样人？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 15,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_34",
      "block_index": 34,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "奴本是落难人奔走天涯。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "反二黄慢板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_35",
      "block_index": 35,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "听你之言，你是被难之人，意欲带你去见我家母亲。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 23,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_36",
      "block_index": 36,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "但凭小姐。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 5,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_37",
      "block_index": 37,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "丫鬟带路。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 5,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_38",
      "block_index": 38,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "她本是落难人来到我家，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "西皮摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_39",
      "block_index": 39,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "不由我一阵阵心内如麻。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_40",
      "block_index": 40,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "叫丫鬟忙带路后堂以下，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_41",
      "block_index": 41,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "有请母亲。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 5,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_42",
      "block_index": 42,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（邹母上。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 6,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_43",
      "block_index": 43,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹母",
      "text": "我的儿请为娘有何根芽？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹母",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "西皮摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_44",
      "block_index": 44,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "参见母亲。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 5,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_45",
      "block_index": 45,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹母",
      "text": "罢了。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 3,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹母",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_46",
      "block_index": 46,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "启禀母亲：孩儿花园游玩，得一难女，母亲请看。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 22,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_47",
      "block_index": 47,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹母",
      "text": "待我看来。原来是一被难之人，叫她前来见我。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 5,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹母",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_49",
      "block_index": 49,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "难女前来见过母亲。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 9,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_50",
      "block_index": 50,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "叩见老夫人。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 6,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "旦"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_51",
      "block_index": 51,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹母",
      "text": "那一难女因何到此？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 9,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹母",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_52",
      "block_index": 52,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "呀！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 2,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_53",
      "block_index": 53,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "老夫人问我的真情实话，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "西皮摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_54",
      "block_index": 54,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "泄机关又恐怕被人所杀。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_55",
      "block_index": 55,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "不由人一霎时为难心下，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_56",
      "block_index": 56,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "有了。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 3,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_57",
      "block_index": 57,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "陈杏元改换了汪月英，哄骗与她。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 15,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "西皮摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_58",
      "block_index": 58,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹母",
      "text": "那一女子，为何背地沉吟？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 12,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹母",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_59",
      "block_index": 59,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "难女怎敢背地沉吟。夫人、小姐请高坐，听难女一言告禀。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 26,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_60",
      "block_index": 60,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "尊夫人与小姐听奴言讲，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "西皮慢板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_61",
      "block_index": 61,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "细听我落难人叙说端详：",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_62",
      "block_index": 62,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "家住在扬州郡江都小县，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_63",
      "block_index": 63,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "奴姓汪名月英父母在堂。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_64",
      "block_index": 64,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "都只为雁门关打了败仗，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_65",
      "block_index": 65,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "恨卢杞命杏元去和番邦。选美女四十名一同——",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_67",
      "block_index": 67,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "前往，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 3,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "西皮二六板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_68",
      "block_index": 68,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "有小女在其内离了故乡。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_69",
      "block_index": 69,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "到他国不过是下贱之样，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_70",
      "block_index": 70,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "奴投在落雁坡一命身亡。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_71",
      "block_index": 71,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "蒙神圣保佑我性命未丧，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_72",
      "block_index": 72,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "又谁知落在了夫人花墙。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_73",
      "block_index": 73,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "尊夫人、贤小姐听奴言讲：",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 12,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_74",
      "block_index": 74,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "奴情愿为使女又待何妨。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_75",
      "block_index": 75,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹母",
      "text": "听伊言来泪悲伤，骂声卢杞狗奸党！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 8,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹母",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "西皮摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_77",
      "block_index": 77,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹母",
      "text": "只害得他一家人东逃西往，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 12,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹母",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "哭板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_78",
      "block_index": 78,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "劝母亲免悲泪慈悲心肠。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "西皮摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_79",
      "block_index": 79,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "哎，母亲，我看此女，生的倒也聪明伶俐，何不将她收留府下，做一位螟蛉义女，母亲意下如何？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 43,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_80",
      "block_index": 80,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹母",
      "text": "那一难女，可知我们是甚等样人家？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 16,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹母",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_81",
      "block_index": 81,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "难女不知。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 5,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_82",
      "block_index": 82,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹母",
      "text": "我家老爷现任河南八府巡按，老身受过诰命。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 20,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹母",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_83",
      "block_index": 83,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "原来是一名诰命夫人，小女子不知，多多有罪。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 21,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_84",
      "block_index": 84,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹母",
      "text": "老身有意将你收留府下，做一位螟蛉义女，不知你意下如何？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 27,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹母",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_85",
      "block_index": 85,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "这……",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 3,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_86",
      "block_index": 86,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "还不前来拜见母亲。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 9,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_87",
      "block_index": 87,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "如此，母亲请上，受孩儿一拜！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 14,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_88",
      "block_index": 88,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "喜洋洋近前来双膝跪倒，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "西皮摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_89",
      "block_index": 89,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "尊一声老夫人细听根苗：",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_90",
      "block_index": 90,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "在府中望母亲多多训教，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_91",
      "block_index": 91,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "到后来儿不忘教养恩高。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_92",
      "block_index": 92,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹母",
      "text": "但不知你叫何名字？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 9,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹母",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_93",
      "block_index": 93,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "我叫汪月英。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 6,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_94",
      "block_index": 94,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹母",
      "text": "好。改姓不改名，改为邹月英。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 14,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹母",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_95",
      "block_index": 95,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "多谢母亲起名，但不知小姐青春几何？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 17,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_96",
      "block_index": 96,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹母",
      "text": "一十六岁。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 5,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹母",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_97",
      "block_index": 97,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "奴家二九，占长了。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 9,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_98",
      "block_index": 98,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹母",
      "text": "长则长，幼则幼，二人在这绣楼前，当着老身一拜。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 23,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹母",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_99",
      "block_index": 99,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "叫姐姐你请上受我一拜，我与你好一比一母同胎。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "西皮摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_101",
      "block_index": 101,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "小姐请上，受愚姐一拜。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_102",
      "block_index": 102,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "近前来把贤妹一生高叫，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "西皮摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_103",
      "block_index": 103,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "为姐的有一言细听根苗：",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_104",
      "block_index": 104,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "在府中早晚间多多看照，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_105",
      "block_index": 105,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "咱二人犹如那一母同胞。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_106",
      "block_index": 106,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹母",
      "text": "叫丫鬟将酒宴后堂摆好，母女们饮一个快乐逍遥。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹母",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "西皮摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_108",
      "block_index": 108,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（邹母下。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 6,
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_109",
      "block_index": 109,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "叫姐姐休得要珠泪嚎啕，我与你好一似一母同胞。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "西皮摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_111",
      "block_index": 111,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "蒙夫人与小姐恩高义好，今日里在邹府独自逍遥。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "西皮摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_113",
      "block_index": 113,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "姐姐走吓！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 5,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_114",
      "block_index": 114,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "请。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 2,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_115",
      "block_index": 115,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "背转思贤公子珠泪垂掉，我的梅……",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "西皮摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_117",
      "block_index": 117,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "姐姐“梅”什么？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 8,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_118",
      "block_index": 118,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "看梅花开的茂盛。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 8,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_119",
      "block_index": 119,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "嗳，姐姐喜爱梅花？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 9,
      "speaker_name_raw": "邹云英",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_120",
      "block_index": 120,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_陈杏元",
      "text": "正是。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 3,
      "speaker_name_raw": "陈杏元",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 3
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_121",
      "block_index": 121,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_邹云英",
      "text": "明日命丫鬟采来梅花，与姐姐玩耍。",
